OL,3,CJill Biden says she feared Joe Biden
OL,4,Cwas having a stroke during 2024 debate
OL,6,FFormer first lady Jill Biden feared
OL,7,Fher husband, then US President Joe
OL,8,FBiden, was having a stroke during his
OL,9,Fdisastrous June 2024 debate
OL,10,Fperformance.
OL,12,FBiden's infamous debate against Donald
OL,13,FTrump fuelled fears among voters that
OL,14,Fhe was too old for a second term, and
OL,15,Fultimately led to the end of his re-
OL,16,Felection campaign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
