OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779973867
OL,3,CJill Biden says she feared Joe Biden
OL,4,Cwas having a stroke during 2024 debate
OL,6,F"I was frightened, because I had never
OL,7,Fever seen Joe like that before or
OL,8,Fsince. Never," Jill Biden told CBS
OL,9,FNews in an interview, which is due to
OL,10,Fair on Sunday.
OL,12,F"I don't know what happened," she
OL,13,Fsaid. "As I watched it, I thought,
OL,14,F'Oh, my God, he's having a stroke.'
OL,15,FAnd it scared me to death."
OL,17,FBiden, then 81 and facing concerns
OL,18,Fabout his age and health, was shaky,
OL,19,Fmumbling, and sometimes scarcely
OL,20,Faudible during the debate.
OL,26,@pD@NO]tD@AOUtD@]O]uD@GOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
