OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779973867
OL,3,CJill Biden says she feared Joe Biden
OL,4,Cwas having a stroke during 2024 debate
OL,6,FHe failed to fact-check Trump during
OL,7,Fthe debate, who went on to win the
OL,8,Felection and return to the White House.
OL,10,FDemocrats already had questions about
OL,11,Fhis fitness, and his attempts to
OL,12,Fexplain away his performance and to
OL,13,Freassure voters that he could handle
OL,14,Ffour more years of the demanding job
OL,15,Fdid little to assuage them.
OL,17,FIn a post-debate event that night,
OL,18,FJill Biden said, "Joe, you did such a
OL,19,Fgreat job. You answered every
OL,20,Fquestion. You knew all the facts."
OL,26,@zD@ROU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
