OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779973867
OL,3,CJill Biden says she feared Joe Biden
OL,4,Cwas having a stroke during 2024 debate
OL,6,FBiden's aides insisted the debate was
OL,7,Fan anomaly ` one bad night from an
OL,8,Fageing, but still energetic and
OL,9,Fcompetent, president.
OL,11,FShortly afterwards, Biden acknowledged
OL,12,Fhe was "not a young man. I don't walk
OL,13,Fas easily as I used to. I don't talk
OL,14,Fas smoothly as I used to. I don't
OL,15,Fdebate as well as I used to."
OL,26,@tD@HOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
