OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779973867
OL,3,CJill Biden says she feared Joe Biden
OL,4,Cwas having a stroke during 2024 debate
OL,6,FBut in late July - less than four
OL,7,Fweeks after the debate and under
OL,8,Fmounting pressure from within his
OL,9,Fparty, he stepped aside, and threw his
OL,10,Fsupport behind his vice president,
OL,11,FKamala Harris.
OL,13,FJill Biden's interview comes as she
OL,14,Fprepares to kick off a book tour to
OL,15,Fpromote View from the East Wing, her
OL,16,Fforthcoming memoir about her time in
OL,17,Fthe White House.
OL,19,FITV News' US partner, CNN, said a
OL,20,FBiden spokesperson declined to comment
OL,21,Fabout Jill Biden's CBS interview.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
